      <h1>RPG Schedule</h1>
      <p>A discord bot for posting game announcements for RPGs. Features include:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Web interface for posting and editing game announcements</li>
        <li>Automated or manual sign ups and automated waitlisting</li>
        <li>Automated rescheduling (daily, weekly, biweekly, or monthly)</li>
        <li>Automated reminders</li>
        <li>RSS Feed</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Note:</strong> Games are automatically pruned 48 - 72 hours after the scheduled time. Or you can delete them manually.</p>
